{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nClass attributes, like these:\r\n\r\n    class foo { my $.index = 0; method bar{ $.index++ }}; say foo.new.bar for ^3\r\n    #OUTPUT: «0␤1␤2␤»\r\n\r\nand [explained in the synopsis](https://design.perl6.org/S12.html#___top) are not commented.\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nExpand [this section](https://docs.perl6.org/language/classtut#State) to include them. Or add another section.\r\n",
